#. STRINGS.UI.KALTSIT_ESPERANTA_SKILL.LEVEL_DESC.3.1
msgctxt "STRINGS.UI.KALTSIT_ESPERANTA_SKILL.LEVEL_DESC.3.1"
msgid "Attack Range changes, and Mon3tr Moves to the position of the Reconstruction. ATK +200%, Block +2, Max HP +5000, Attack Interval reduces, loses 80 HP per second, attacks all blocked enemies, attacks deal True damage and heal self for 50% ATK. When skill ends or letha damage is taken, Mon3tr returns to her original position"
msgstr "解除手持装备，吸收重构体武器最高10%的耐久转为基础攻击力\n普通攻击时对附近造成300%基础攻击力的真实伤害\n生命上限+5000，每秒流失80点生命值\n攻击时治疗自身基础攻击力100%的生命。\n技能结束或受到致命伤害时，返回初始位置"

#. STRINGS.UI.KALTSIT_ESPERANTA_SKILL.LEVEL_DESC.3.2
msgctxt "STRINGS.UI.KALTSIT_ESPERANTA_SKILL.LEVEL_DESC.3.2"
msgid "Attack Range changes, and Mon3tr Moves to the position of the Reconstruction. ATK +200%, Block +2, Max HP +5000, Attack Interval reduces, loses 80 HP per second, attacks all blocked enemies, attacks deal True damage and heal self for 50% ATK. When skill ends or letha damage is taken, Mon3tr returns to her original position"
msgstr "解除手持装备，攻击范围改变，若有重构体\n则移动至重构体位置，攻击力+200%，攻击\n间隔降低，生命上限+500，每秒流失16点\n生命值，同时攻击附近所有敌人，伤害类型\n变为真实，攻击治疗自身相当于攻击力50%\n的生命。技能期间每次攻击都会恢复附近最\n多3位友军相当于攻击力100%生命\n技能结束或受到致命伤害时，返回初始位置"

